menuItemRecipes.name: Cheese Burger
menuItemRecipes.description: Cheese burger with Special Sauce, Lettuce, and Sliced Onions
menuItemRecipes.prepInstruction:
Toast Buns
Sauce up the buns
Melt cheese over 2 patties and place on bottom bun
Put Lettuce an onions and on top of patties 
Place top bun
